Act and 29 CFR §§ 3.3 and 3.4 require the contractor or subcontractor to fi=
le a
weekly “Statement of Compliance”. 29 CFR § 5.5(a)(3)(ii) requires, as a
contract stipulation, that the contractor submit weekly to the contracting
agency a copy of all payrolls, along with a weekly “Statement of Compliance=
”.
Contractors may use Optional Form WH-347, available at </span><a
