style=3D'font-size:12.0pt'>In the case of larger contracts, such as for air=
ports,
highways, or dams, the “site of the work” is necessarily more extensive and=
 may
include the whole area in which the construction activity will take place.<=
/span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph><span style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115=
