</span></span><span style=3D'font-size:12.0pt'>Not included in the ”site of=
 the work”
are permanent home offices, branch plant establishments, fabrication plants,
and tool yards, etc. of a contractor or subcontractor whose locations and
continuance in operation are determined wholly without regard to a particul=
ar
Federal or federally-assisted contract or project. </span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph><span style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115=
%'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph style=3D'margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin=
-bottom:
0in;margin-left:1.0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal'><span
