fabrication plants, batch plants, borrow pits, job headquarters, tool yards,
etc, of a commercial or material supplier which are established by a suppli=
er
of materials for the project before opening of bids and not on the site of =
the
work as stated in 29 CFR § 5.2(l)(1), even where such operations for a peri=
od
of time may be dedicated exclusively, or nearly so, to the performance of a
contract.</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph style=3D'margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001p=
t;
