contained in other Davis-Bacon Related Acts. Therefore, if a construction
project is funded under multiple statutes, including one with a pre-existing
Davis-Bacon related Act provision as well as ARRA, then the ARRA prevailing
wage requirement applies if any such ARRA assistance is provided for the
project.</span></p>

