line-height:normal'><span style=3D'font-size:12.0pt'>Timekeepers who perfor=
m no
manual labor on construction projects are not considered to be “laborers” o=
r “mechanics”
for purposes of DBRA. However, if such workers perform other duties as labo=
rers
or mechanics, they must be paid the WD rate for the particular classificati=
on
involved for the time so spent.</span></p>

