</span></span><span style=3D'font-size:12.0pt'>Truck drivers transporting
materials or supplies between a facility that is deemed part of the site of=
 the
work and the actual construction site.</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph><span style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115=
