<span
style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><span
style=3D'font-size:12.0pt'>If an employee should terminate prior to becoming
eligible under a vacation or sick leave plan, and amounts have been paid in=
to
an account on such employee’s behalf for which the contractor has taken cre=
dit
towards meeting its prevailing wage obligations, then the employee must be =
paid
